## Learning about R

Key to developing a good understanding of R is to get access to a basic set of tools (i.e. skills and knowledge) that quickly enable to learn more by:

- Asking the right questions
- Looking at what others have done
- Fixing errors and improving functionality in your own programs
- Some suggestions: [Advanced R programming](http://adv-r.had.co.nz) by Hadley Wickham

