## Suggestions for further reading
- Look at what others have done on GitHub
- Browse through _one_ R book: "Advanced R programming" by Hadley Wickham
- Make yourself familiar with StackOverflow and browse through some questions on your favorite topic
- Start simple by solving simple statistical problems and work your way up

